Note that I've updated Travis not to directly pass in the branch name through the `--version` arg. This is because if the `--version` tag is not provided, then `get_default_version()` is already called, which already gets the branch name -- so using the `--version` tag is not necessary.

Additionally, `get_default_version()` automatically replaces the `/` and `-` characters in branch names, allowing branches such as this one (`dependabot/pip/psutil-5.6.6`) to be built.

